{"title":"The Made in Germany Nicolai Bikes Argon GX Gravel Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/02/the-made-in-germany-nicolai-bikes-argon-gx-gravel-bike/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-made-in-germany-nicolai-bikes-argon-gx-gravel-bike","date":1614008451000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1780\" height=\"1187\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206090\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1780&amp;quality=75 1780w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1780px) 100vw, 1780px\" /></p>\n<p>These days, gravel bike designs can be very redundant, something German manufacturers like Nicolai Bikes are looking to overcome. Their newest design, the Argon GX, is as much a gravel bike as it is a touring bike but look closely for some clever manufacturing detailing. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206091\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></p>\n<p>Through 3D modeling and engineering, Nicolai is able to construct durable and lightweight  7020-T6 frame components. Each of these pieces are made on modern 5-axis CNC machines and allows for the construction of so-called &#8220;Hollow Mill&#8221; assemblages. The bottom bracket and chainstay yoke in the Argon CX use this technology to both shed weight and set their offerings apart from their competitors.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1120\" height=\"1120\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206092\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1120&amp;quality=75 1120w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1120\" height=\"1120\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-206093\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1120&amp;quality=75 1120w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px\" /></p>\n<p>Other details include the option for a Pinion gear box, fender/rack mounts, flat mount disc calipers, internal routing, and designed geometries to fit just about any body type. Head to <a href=\"https://en.nicolai-bicycles.com/bike/argon-gx/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Nicolai</a> to see more!</p>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"b2cecb17fca9dc75be337cff6223cffe6b6e962c86a2d5e2474490de2e3c6676","category":"Cycling"}